<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>事务 on 演示站点</title><link>https://example.com/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1/</link><description>Recent content in 事务 on 演示站点</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>Example Person</copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:32:48 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://example.com/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>事务的定义</title><link>https://example.com/p/%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:32:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://example.com/p/%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="事务">事务
&lt;/h1>&lt;p>把多操作绑定在一起，如果一个操作失败则全部操作失败，数据回滚。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="例子">例子
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">db&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">Transaction&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kd">func&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">tx&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">gorm&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">DB&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">error&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// 在事务中执行一些 db 操作（从这里开始，您应该使用 &amp;#39;tx&amp;#39; 而不是 &amp;#39;db&amp;#39;）
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">err&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">:=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">tx&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">Create&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Animal&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;Giraffe&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}).&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Error&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">err&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">!=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">nil&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// 返回任何错误都会回滚事务
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">err&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
